Now look at him.

178
00:25:52,148 --> 00:25:53,856
Yes, I intend to.

179
00:25:55,648 --> 00:25:57,564
- What happened?
- He fell!

180
00:25:58,356 --> 00:26:00,148
He falls.

181
00:26:09,023 --> 00:26:10,939
