a very severe fall.

182
00:26:12,439 --> 00:26:15,189
He's a clumsy soul.

183
00:26:16,272 --> 00:26:18,189
Never looks where he's going.

184
00:26:18,272 --> 00:26:22,522
But that's all right.
He has me to take care of him.

185
00:26:22,606 --> 00:26:25,356
