in the isolation ward, will you?

220
00:30:05,272 --> 00:30:06,980
Yes, sir.

221
00:30:08,647 --> 00:30:11,397
Don't be frightened.
He won't hurt you.

222
00:30:12,730 --> 00:30:14,939
