247
00:32:17,439 --> 00:32:19,355
Please forgive me.

248
00:32:20,189 --> 00:32:22,564
- You all right?
- Yes, sir.

249
00:32:24,022 --> 00:32:26,980
Please ask Mrs. Mothershead
to come up here.

250
00:32:27,022 --> 00:32:30,439
